OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FUK seeks talks with Fujitsu
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fon Horizon scandal         
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Business secretary Kemi Badenoch has   
OL,6, requested urgent talks with Fujitsu on 
OL,7, compensation for sub-postmasters caught
OL,8, up in the Post Office Horizon scandal. 
OL,10,FAn inquiry is ongoing into how hundreds
OL,11,Fof sub-postmasters were wrongly        
OL,12,Fconvicted due to faulty software.      
OL,14,FOnce the inquiry has "established all  
OL,15,Fthe facts", then the government will   
OL,16,Fact, a spokesperson said.              
OL,18,FIt comes after Fujitsu Europe's boss   
OL,19,Fsaid the firm has a "moral obligation" 
OL,20,Fto provide compensation.               
